sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    box #4682B4 Backend
        participant API as API Gateway
        participant DB as Database
    end
    actor User
    User->>API: Login request
    activate API
    API->>+DB: Query user
    Note over API,DB: Auth flow
    DB-->>-API: User record
    alt valid credentials
        API-->>User: 200 OK
    else invalid
        API-->>User: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    deactivate API
